</ol>
<ul>
<li>6.0系列无广告：<a href="https://dl.bandisoft.com/bandizip/BANDIZIP-SETUP.EXE">官方安装版</a>、<a href="https://dl.bandisoft.com/bandizip/BANDIZIP-PORTABLE-GL-32BIT.ZIP">32位便携版</a>、 <a href="https://dl.bandisoft.com/bandizip/BANDIZIP-PORTABLE-GL-64BIT.ZIP">64位便携版</a></li>
</ul>
